<paragraph id="3C1A36EDE6323C26FF7C0719FC27FE85" blockId="7.[136,1452,320,450]" pageId="7" pageNumber="288">
Diagnosis:—The new species is easily distinguished from 
<taxonomicName id="FBA54D6EE6323C26FD4A0719FCDCFEAA" box="[702,827,320,341]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Oreocharis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="288" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="jasminina">
