<figureCitation id="A49E2A68E6323C26FCA0073DFC85FE86" box="[852,866,356,377]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="2.[136,229,1338,1360]" captionTargetBox="[228,1357,199,1303]" captionTargetId="figure-21@2.[222,1366,190,1314]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 2. Oreocharis hainanensis S.J.Ling &amp; M.X. Ren sp. nov. A. Habit; B. abaxial leaf surface; C. lateral view of corolla, sepal and calyx; D. front view of corolla; E. opening corolla showing stamens and staminode; F. pistil, stamens and staminode; G. capsule; H. seed. (Drawn by Shu-Ping Guan based on the holotype S.J.Ling 2020091701 in HUTB)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6340389" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6340389/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="288">2</figureCitation>
